J35QVDZRZCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2F3QFL2WTEPZKIU6RJ35QVDZRZCI%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7kigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=4c8ca73d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2F3QFL2WTEPZKIU6RJ35QVDZRZCI%2F&h=b6fe81aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200519/3QFL2WTEPZKIU6RJ35QVDZRZCI/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"佢都知套野垃圾唔敢放係新聞台播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"332好少播紀錄片 00分直播30分重播<br />\n不過有時會重播經緯線嘅"},{"pid":"6f1476561617476a0e04a832ac7ba4ffc44cacc7","tid":2024767,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>now台好黃</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每次見呢句都笑出黎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢句：<br />\n<br />\n查下當年碌柒起家支銀點大撐佢，同8號仔背後幾多支那估東囉！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9402f0286f93bb35a44a4aacf5f9019c38d44d67","tid":2024767,"uid":114701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"中央視免費就要播咩？<br />\n香港d製作人都無風骨嘅，<br />\n呢d癲倒事非垃圾片不值浪費airtime啦，<br />\n賣多幾個廣告仲好啦<br />\n講真，中聯辦d線眼已經深入各大電視台，<br />\n要控制思想，就必先要用傳媒維穩<br />\n所以你見到大台愈來愈多央視片<br />\n想繼續發牌嗎？  咪要播埋呢d囉，黃都無計"}]}